quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  67,13,"Suu…óee onon …ìee yim…ìe, konngu…ói mon maa fe√±√±inon …ói. Allah kan hino anndi fii majji. Kanko senii…óo On, himo anndi ko woni e …ìer…óe jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Huunde e …óum suu…óaaki Mo."
  67,14,"E hara tagu…óo taguuli …óin fof On anndaa sirru e ko …ìuri sirru wirnaade? Ko Kanko le woni Newanii…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Humpitii…óo fiyakuuji ma…ì…ìe. Huunde suu…óaaki Mo e …óin."
  67,15,"Ko Kanko wa…óani on leydi ndin eltaandi newiniraa ka ho…óee : haray yahee e seraaji mayri, √±aamon e arsike Makko mo O hebilani on e mayri. Ko ka Makko tun woni ummital fii √±aaweede njo…ìdi."
  67,16,"E on hooli wonnde Allah won…óo On ka kammu nde fettinta leydi e mo'on leydi ndin wano O mutiniri Qaaruuna e mayri? Hari le ko ndi newinanoondi fii ho…óugol e mun. Tawaa yoo hindi dilla e mon …ìaawo ndi dee∆¥ude."
  67,17,"Kaa on hooli wonnde Allah won…óo ka kammu On nde O accitataa kaa∆¥e e mo'on immorde ka kammu, wano O accitirnoo …óen e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon, tuma yi'oton lette Am …óen. Ko woni tun, on nafitoroytaa …óum …ìaawo nde yi'oyton lette …óen."
  67,18,"Sellii wonnde mofte adinoo…ìe …ìen sirkoo…ìe …óon …ìen fenniino, lette Allah …óen yani e ma…ì…ìe fewndo …ìe ha…ì…ìitinoo e yeddugol fenna. Taskii ko honno lette Am …óen wattinirnoo e ma…ì…ìe ! ∆äum wonuno lette sattu…óe."
  67,19,"E …ìee fennoo…ìe yi'aali colli …óin dow ma…ì…ìe, tuma …ói wiirata, …ói fontay gabitannji majji …óin e henndu ndun, …ói √±obba …ói kadi? Wonnde ko Allah jogitii …óin fii wata …ói yanu ka leydi. Pellet, Kanko ko O reenu…óo kala huunde. Hay huunde suu…óaaki Mo."
  67,20,"Konuujo alanaa on onon …ìee heefer…ìe …ìe, mo no da…óana on e lette Allah …óen tuma O faandanii on …óe. Tigi on, heefer…ìe …ìen wonaali si wanaa hodaa…ìe; ko seytaane hodi …ìe, …ìe …óaynitori mo."
  67,21,"Alaa arsikoowo on si Allah jogitike ko O arsikata on kon. Si ko woni, heefer…ìe …ìen duumi e ∆¥aggere e townitaare, e salagol goonga."
  67,22,"Kere ko on yaaroowo no hippi yeeso mun, e maanaa sirkoowo on …ìuri feewude? Kaa ko gom…óin…óo yahoowo on no √±ii…ìi e laawol focciingol?"
  67,23,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe : ko Allah woni tagu…óo on, O wa…óani on nan…óe …óe naniron, e gii…óe e yi'iron, e …ìer…óe …óe haqqiliron. Kono fan…óii ko yettoton Mo e ko O neeminiri on kon."
  67,24,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe : Ko Allah woni saakit…óo on e leydi ndin, wanaa sanamuuji mon …ói tagataa …óin hay fus ! Kadi, ko ka Makko tun woni moo…ìitoyte…óon √ëalnde Darngal, fii √±aaweede yo…ìitee, wanaa ka sanamuuji mon. Hulee Mo kisan, rewon Mo Kanko tun."
  67,25,"∆Åee fennoo…ìe ummital no wi'a : ko honnde tuma woni fii ndee fodoore nde fodu-…óaa men an Muhammadu e wonndii…ìe maa …ìen, si tawii ko on goongu…ìe e kon nodditi…óon wi'ugol nde aray?"
  67,26,"Maakan …ìe yo Nulaa…óo : Anndee anndugol fii Darngal, ko ka Allah woni. Hay gooto anndaa nde ngal darotoo si wanaa Kanko. Min on ko mi jertiniinoowo tun …ìannginana on jertinaango am."